<chapter xml:id="db_pil_wui_taskHistoryView" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    version="5.1" xml:lang="en-US">
    <title>Working with Scheduler Activities</title>
    <para>The following sections describe how to work with schedulers. You can use the actions described in the following sections to track the execution of Quartz Scheduler tasks The following actions are supported for the <guilabel>Scheduler Activities</guilabel> view:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para><xref linkend="display_scheduler_activities"/></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><xref linkend="display_scheduler_activity_details"/></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><xref linkend="filter_scheduler_activities"/></para>
        </listitem>        
    </itemizedlist>
    <sect1 xml:id="display_scheduler_activities">
        <title>Listing Scheduler Activities</title>
        <para>The workspace of the of the <guilabel>Scheduler Activity</guilabel> view documents the execution of Quartz scheduler tasks.</para>
        <mediaobject><alt>Screenshot Scheduler Activities View</alt><imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="images/scr_schedulerActivitiesView.png" width="14cm"/>
            </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
        <para>The overview table displays the following information for each scheduler activity by default:</para>
        <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>ID</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>The unique identifier of the scheduler activity (sequential number).</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Group</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Quartz task group.</para>

                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Name</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Scheduler activity.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>State</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>State information. The valid values depend on the type. The following values are currently supported for the types <guilabel>maintask</guilabel> and <guilabel>importtask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>STARTED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>FINISHED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>FAILED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>INTERRUPTED</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported for the type <guilabel>applicationtask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>SHUTDOWN</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>STARTUP</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported for the type <guilabel>timertask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>ACTIVATED</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>DEACTIVATED</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>

            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Type</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>maintask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>applicationtask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>importtask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>timertask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Task</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Quartz task to which the scheduler activity is linked.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Created</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Indicates the date and time (timestamp) when the scheduler activity was created.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
    </sect1>
    <sect1 xml:id="display_scheduler_activity_details">
        <title>Displaying Scheduler Activity Information</title>
        <para>You can display the details for a specific scheduler activity in the details pane. Compared to the overview table the details pane contains more information (context).</para>
        <mediaobject><alt>Scheduler Activities view with details</alt><imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="images/scr_schedulerActivitiesViewDetails.png" align="left"
                    width="15cm" format="PNG"/>
            </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
        <para>The following information is currently available in the details view:</para>
        <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>ID</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>The unique identifier of the scheduler activity (sequential number).</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Group</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Quartz task group.</para>

                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Name</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Scheduler activity.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>State</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>State information. The valid values depend on the type. The following values are currently supported for the types <guilabel>maintask</guilabel> and <guilabel>importtask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>STARTED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>FINISHED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>FAILED</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>INTERRUPTED</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported for the type <guilabel>applicationtask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>SHUTDOWN</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>STARTUP</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported for the type <guilabel>timertask</guilabel>:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>ACTIVATED</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>DEACTIVATED</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>

            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Type</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>The following values are currently supported:</para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>maintask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>applicationtask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>importtask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><guilabel>timertask</guilabel></para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Task</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Name of the Quartz task to which the scheduler activity is linked.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Context</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Varpool key. Unique identifier of the process activity to which the scheduler activity is mapped (for more information, see <xref linkend="db_pil_wui_processesView"/>)).</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term><guilabel>Created</guilabel></term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>Indicates the date and time (timestamp) when the scheduler activity was created.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
    </sect1>
    <sect1 xml:id="filter_scheduler_activities">
        <title>Filtering Scheduler Activities</title>
        <para>You can filter the existing scheduler activities by ID (simple filter) or by other parameters (for more information about filter criteria, see <xref
                linkend="db_pil_wui_filterSettings"/>). A detailed description of the simple filter functionality can be found in <xref linkend="basic_filter"/>. A detailed description of the steps for advanced filter configurations can be found in <xref
                linkend="advanced_filter"/>.</para>
    </sect1>
</chapter>